<br />
This goes against what was posted by SOE.  Perhaps currently all nerfed additions to the table are set to the same value, but I see no reason to disbelieve what they stated about being able to adjust mobs independantly.  At least from a technical standpoint.
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Well of course this new "charmed damage table" feature isnt OoW only, but for all future content. Why would the cook up such a complicated change for just 1 expansion. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
