I also expect it to be added to all new content, but I didn't think that would apply to new mobs in very old zones.  We're talking velious here.  Level 60 mobs.  This is a zone where you could charm something with allure for more dps than the mobs I'm talking about, that simply doesn't make sense.  And honestly, this is a very minor change in regards to actual development work needed.  One additional database field and one extra step in damage calculations.
<br />

